column1:
Better than all right! Feels great knowin' we put
that asswipe in his place!

If what we just saw actually happened in the
past...

Then, Akira Konoe escaped an abusive
childhood and avenged his mother by killing
his own father.

He must have framed the entire thing as a
robbery in order to avoid suspicion.
You're sayin' he's a victim of some high 'n' mighty shitbag, too?

He must've felt so trapped... There was nobody
he could turn to.
So he set out to become his own hero...

And the power to change hearts helped him do
just that.

It's just too sad! There had to be another way!
There just had to!

Whatever his past was, it doesn't justify what
he's doing now.

Nothing makes it okay for him to take control
of people against their will.

If we don't stop him now, more and more
people are gonna get hurt.
You're all thinking the same thing, aren't you?
We need to change his heart.
Sure. But you're all still set on doing this, right?

Right. If we don't stop him here, then nothing's
ever going to change.
Let's do everything we can for now.
While it's true we need to change Konoe's heart, let's not forget we also need to save those whose Desires he's stolen.
Then, it's time we bust out the calling card!
Oh, yeah... That's kinda your thing, isn't it?

Yeah! We'll change his heart and take back
everyone's Desires!

Okay, let's head back to the car and come up
with a plan!
